title: Tzar
description: Strategy of real time with an impurity of role elements. Action of game occurs in the world approximately corresponding the real historical period between 500 and 1000 of our era. Lonely hero-mercenary Horatio has an opportunity to operate own group, to collect resources, to develop economy, to open new technologies, to be at war and agree with the states of opponents - differently, to be engaged in all in what king or the sultan independent medieval usually was engaged
